Taken from the Dutch national television channel NPO Cultura broadcast, June 12, 2016.

This was broadcast twice the same day, but both had some errors. This torrent includes the second broadcast from which the error was deleted. At the 15:48 mark the recording all of a sudden started again from the beginning, went into fast forward for 42 seconds and then continued playing normally but repeating almost 9 minutes. This has all been cut out.
The tracktitles were shown on the screen during the first broadcast.
